# All timestamps must be in UTC (e.g. Brussels = UTC+1, so 10:00 local = 09:00 UTC)

### **Get Access Token for Waterside - ADMIN**
POST http://localhost:8180/realms/mineralflow/protocol/openid-connect/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

client_id=waterside-client&
client_secret=mi7FZ0OskRoryIEhaHsXfnvE6jB2Si65&
username=adam&
password=admin&
grant_type=password

> {%
    client.global.set("admin_access_token", response.body.access_token);
%}

### **Get Access Token for Waterside - SHIP_CAPTAIN**
POST http://localhost:8180/realms/mineralflow/protocol/openid-connect/token
